      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Don't let outdated methods hold you back</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Join forward-thinking UK businesses using AI-powered wellbeing assessments</p>
      </div>
